      <title>AS下载插件|使用Parcelable接口</title>
      <link href="/2018/10/08/AS%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8CParcelable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3/"/>
      <url>/2018/10/08/AS%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8CParcelable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;今天回顾上周的一些开发任务，结合主管审查代码之后提出的一些建议，对代码进行一些整理，看到一条这样的：</p><blockquote><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;<span class="keyword">import</span> com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName</span><br><span class="line">&gt;<span class="keyword">data</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">CurrencReviewEntity</span></span>(</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>可以考虑替换为实现<code>Parcelable</code>接口</p><p>新写的实体类，如果不是工具生成，可以直接用kotlin写，然后用<code>Option + T</code>快捷键自动实现<code>Parcelable</code>接口</p></blockquote><p>&emsp;&emsp;原来的代码中使用了<code>SerializedName</code>注解来对JSON数据实体类进行映射，主管给出的建议中要求使用Parcelable接口来实现</p><p>&emsp;&emsp;我打开实体类点了几次<code>Option + T</code>没有任何反应，原来是要再下载一个插件<code>Android Parcelable code generator</code>，遂打开AS的preferences，然后查找插件进行下载：<br><img src="https://github.com/EndeRHoshI/Photo/blob/master/blog/AS%20parcelable%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6.png?raw=true" alt=""></p><p>&emsp;&emsp;却弹出了如下错误：<br><img src="https://github.com/EndeRHoshI/Photo/blob/master/blog/%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%87%BA%E9%94%99.png?raw=true" alt=""></p><p>&emsp;&emsp;懒得去设置代理地址了，所以直接去jetbrains的插件官网：<a href="https://plugins.jetbrains.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://plugins.jetbrains.com/</a> 搜索下载好，然后解压到AS/Contents/plugins目录下</p><p>&emsp;&emsp;然后再重启AS，大功告成，我们可以点击实体类名右侧的空白，用快捷键自动补全试试：<br><img src="https://github.com/EndeRHoshI/Photo/blob/master/blog/AS%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%7C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Parcelable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0Parcelable%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3.png?raw=true" alt=""></p><p>&emsp;&emsp;然后代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Keep</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">data class <span class="title">TickerCommentResponse</span> <span class="params">(</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">    @SerializedName(<span class="string">"success"</span>)</span> var success: Boolean,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    @<span class="title">SerializedName</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">"error"</span>)</span> var error: String,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    @<span class="title">SerializedName</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">"errorCode"</span>)</span> var errorCode: Int,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    @<span class="title">SerializedName</span><span class="params">(<span class="string">"data"</span>)</span> var data: TickerCommentBean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">) : Parcelable </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  constructor(parcel: Parcel) : <span class="keyword">this</span>(</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.readByte() != <span class="number">0</span>.toByte(),</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.readString(),</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.readInt(),</span><br><span class="line">    TODO(<span class="string">"data"</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">override fun <span class="title">writeToParcel</span><span class="params">(parcel: Parcel, flags: Int)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.writeByte(<span class="keyword">if</span> (success) <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.writeString(error)</span><br><span class="line">    parcel.writeInt(errorCode)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">override fun <span class="title">describeContents</span><span class="params">()</span>: Int </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  companion object CREATOR : Parcelable.Creator&lt;TickerCommentResponse&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">override fun <span class="title">createFromParcel</span><span class="params">(parcel: Parcel)</span>: TickerCommentResponse </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> TickerCommentResponse(parcel)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">override fun <span class="title">newArray</span><span class="params">(size: Int)</span>: Array&lt;TickerCommentResponse?&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> arrayOfNulls(size)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;因为这里的TickerCommentBean是另一个实体类，所以我们再把constructor处修改好就可以了：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">constructor(parcel: Parcel) : <span class="keyword">this</span>(</span><br><span class="line">  parcel.readByte() != <span class="number">0</span>.toByte(),</span><br><span class="line">  parcel.readString(),</span><br><span class="line">  parcel.readInt(),</span><br><span class="line">  parcel.readParcelable(TickerCommentBean::<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>.<span class="title">java</span>.<span class="title">classLoader</span>))</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;注意这里的TickerCommentBean也需要实现Parcelable接口，否则报错</p><p>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>到最后发现原来只是快捷键不一样，其实并不需要下载插件就可以直接自动实现Parcelable接口</strong></p>]]></content>
      
